room_title: Escape room "The Frightful Feast" by Room Escape DC in Washington, D.C.
room_description:
You and your teammates wake up in a poorly lit cell and can’t quite remember how you got there. As you come to your senses, you can just make out three monstrous voices planning a party. It seems they’ve decided to have you over for dinner…in a manner of speaking.
The ghastly group has left you unattended for just one hour to attend to the last details of their frightful feast, giving you just sixty minutes to avoid becoming tonight’s main course. Can you escape this disastrous dinner before the next course?
